{"tid":1183090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple 申請無線安全系統專利：可遠程操控iPhone“變磚”","createTime":"2019-06-02T16:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T14:04:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13e70ce7baeff90732bb4d38b057e468b18c2c5d","tid":1183090,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"IT之家6月2日消息 蘋果公司近日申請了一種新的無線安全系統，該系統可以遠程讓被盜的iPhone，iPad或Mac&ldquo;變磚&rdquo;，來打擊蘋果零售店中的盜竊行為<br />\n<br />\n以下是該專利的工作原理：一旦蘋果設備出了安全區域（即蘋果零售店）的邊界，安全系統將提醒附近的管理員（例如零售店員工）。一段時間後，設備將無法再像激活後那樣可以訪問Apple服務，並且按鍵和触摸輸入將被禁用，並不斷嘗試發送其位置。鎖屏上還會顯示一條消息，提醒設備的擁有者將其返還到最近的零售店。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UA0ZB0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUA0ZB0R.jpg&h=bb480956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/426/294.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F426%2F294.htm&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e2ad5388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/426/294.htm</a>"},{"pid":"14402bdd93969f50dcf7f6f283ec5f52f60fc5d7","tid":1183090,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7a79d1de7b59e1ad395eb4ae1c50886c2c5650","tid":1183090,"uid":84128,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"華為近期已掌握變磚技術<br />\n或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"a91c02ff4bac843e44282ff2aa4dcded4b04496e","tid":1183090,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"好正常普通"},{"pid":"a0eda513d3f2baa4ffe4fb32f5e69058a70a956b","tid":1183090,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"應該整成長時間按掣無法啟動(冇電)，變成真正「磚頭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb2fea0f08d025489ab9177620a4c528e688837","